{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_08_03",
  "title": "白石沙季 3話 もっともっと飛躍出来ますように",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そして、現在",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――And now‚ the present.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "それから……あの後、ラジオの収録が始まる直前に\n{user}さんが駆け込んできたんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… after that‚ right before the radio recording started‚\n{user}-san rushed in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6974516623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "スタジオに入ってくるなり「全部揃った！」と叫んで\nディレクターさんに怒られていましたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You shouted‚ \"I got them all!\" as you entered the studio‚\nand got scolded by the director.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さ、最後のとこは忘れてくれ……\n俺も達成感があったから、つい、な……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P‚ please forget that last part…\nI was just so proud of myself‚ I couldn’t help it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.427008573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃はまだロケにも慣れてなくて\n優勝した直後で、かえって混乱していましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I wasn’t used to filming on location‚\nand I was even more flustered right after winning the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.0333342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが、わがままを聞いてくれて\n凄く嬉しかったんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so when {user}-san listened to my selfish request‚\nI was really happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5000008901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、その御朱印帳が見当たらないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I can’t find the goshuincho.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6333335479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの皆の躍進をお祈りしたものだから\n事務所に置いておく方がいいと思ったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was to pray for everyone at Hoshimi Pro to make great strides‚\nso I thought it would be better to keep it at the office‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9333342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "桐箱に入れて、この棚に置いておいたはずなのに\nどこに行ったんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure I put it in this wooden box and left it on this shelf‚\nbut where did it go…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7666675568,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2000,
          "startTime": 51.7666675568
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8733.333333299996,
          "startTime": 58.5000008901
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、皆も掃除の手伝いに来てくれたみたいです\n担当場所を伝えないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ it looks like everyone has come to help with the cleaning.\nI need to tell them their assigned areas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0666690826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "全員分の掃除の割り当てまで考えてあったのか\nやる気も段取りも、沙季はさすがだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You even thought about everyone’s cleaning assignments?\nYour motivation and organization skills are truly impressive‚ Saki…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4000024159,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3899.9984741999897,
          "startTime": 68.3000008901
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、分かりました！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I got it!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5333342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "先週、すずちゃんとこころちゃんが事務所で遊んでて\nはしゃいだ拍子に、こころちゃんが棚にぶつかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Last week‚ Suzu-chan and Kokoro-chan were playing at the office‚\nand Kokoro-chan accidentally bumped into the shelf while they were running around…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9333423614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "その弾みで、棚から箱が落ちたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did the box fall from the shelf because of that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5333416859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、それに驚いたすずちゃんも棚にぶつかって\n棚の物を床に撒いて、莉央さんに怒られたそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Suzu was surprised and also bumped into the shelf‚\nand she scattered things on the floor‚ so Rio-san scolded her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5000090281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……悲しい玉突き事故があったんだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…There was a sad chain reaction accident…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3333416859,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 5666.658314100005,
          "startTime": 95
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "ということは、多分この辺りに……\n……あ、ありました！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That means‚ it’s probably around here somewhere…\n…Ah‚ I found it!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666756947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "床に落ちた拍子に、箱から御朱印帳が飛び出したけど\nそれに気付かないで、箱だけ片付けたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems the goshuincho flew out of the box when it fell on the floor‚\nbut they didn’t notice and just put the box away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6000090281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな\nともかく、見つかって良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nAnyway‚ I’m glad you found it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1666756947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "はい。ふふふ……すずちゃん達には事務所で暴れた分も\n気合いを入れて大掃除をしてもらいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Fufu… I’ll make Suzu and Kokoro put extra effort\ninto cleaning to make up for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3413369711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……ほ、ほどほどにな\n怒られ過ぎてしょげたまま新年を迎えるのも可哀想だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Go easy on them.\nIt would be sad if they started the new year feeling down because they got scolded too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1000090281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "はい。気持ち良く新年を迎えるためにも\n皆でもうひと頑張りしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. To welcome the new year feeling refreshed‚\nlet’s all put in a little more effort.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも、残りの掃除を\nよろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ {user}-san‚ please continue\nwith the rest of the cleaning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6451848234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、頑張ります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay‚ I’ll do my best…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6333330393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そうだ。今年の初詣のロケもそろそろだから\n後でカレンダーを確認しておいてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… that’s right. It’s almost time for the Hatsumōde shoot this year‚\nso please check the calendar later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n今年もロケに呼んでもらえて、良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand.\nI’m glad I got invited to the shoot this year too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "解説役も兼ねられるアイドルってご指名だからな\nしっかり予習しておいてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They requested an idol who could also act as a commentator‚\nso please do your research.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.5833371083
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.5833371083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "――私達は今、星見市の神社に来ています\nここは鎌倉時代まで遡る、由緒ある神社なんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――We are currently at a shrine in Hoshimi City.\nThis is a historic shrine dating back to the Kamakura period.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.8333459218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.5666663726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
