      "text": "……私のお正月の過ごし方ですか？\n以前は確か、月ストの皆と寮にいたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…How did I spend New Year’s?\nWell‚ back then‚ I was at the dorm with the other Moon Tempest members‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1000085195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "年末には出来なかった大掃除をしたんですが……\nデビュー時の映像を見つけて、つい見入ってしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we did the big cleaning we couldn’t finish at the end of the year…\nbut then I found footage from our debut‚ and ended up watching it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.9000085195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.999999706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "「沙季ちゃんでもそんなことあるんだね」……って\n私、そんなにお堅いイメージなんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said‚ “Even Saki-chan has a side like that”…\nDo I really come across as that uptight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.1000085195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.899999706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（以前に比べたら）\n（だいぶTVでも自然に喋れるようになったよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Compared to before‚）\n（she has gotten much better at speaking naturally on TV.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
