    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "今年はお正月に、皆で初詣に来られましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This year‚ we were all able to come for Hatsumōde together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.7333381256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "ついこの間、例の元旦特番のロケがあったので\nなんだか妙な気分ですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We just had the New Year’s special shoot a while ago‚\nso it feels a bit strange…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.9333398183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "でもこの間のロケは、解説しつつ笑いも取って\nTVでも凄く自然に喋ってて良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you did great in the last shoot. You were giving commentary while also being funny‚\nand you were talking so naturally on TV.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.2666772206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.6666795969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "あ、今年も御朱印ちゃんともらって来ましたよ\nこれは事務所に戻ったら、御朱印帳に貼っておきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I got goshuin again this year!\nI’ll paste them in my goshuincho when I get back to the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.7333611805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。初詣に来たんですし\n皆で絵馬も奉納していきませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ since we’re here for Hatsumōde‚\nwhy don’t we all write *ema?（*wooden plaques to write wishes）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.5333723703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、せっかく来たことだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that’s a good idea‚ since we’re here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.5667070626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "それでは……\nうーん、お願い事、どう書こうかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see…\nHmm… what should I wish for…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.4667006173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "前に、御朱印を集めて回った時に比べたら\n神頼みするにしても、だいぶ余裕がありそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Compared to when you were going around collecting goshuin‚\nyou seem much more relaxed about relying on the gods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.7000380196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski028.m4a",
      "text": "……そうでもないですよ\n実を言えば、今、ちょっと焦ってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s not true.\nTo be honest‚ I'm a little anxious right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.3333510079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski029.m4a",
      "text": "サニピがBIG4入りして\n千紗とサニピの皆に、先を行かれている気がして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace has entered BIG4‚\nand I feel like Chisa and the others in Sunny Peace are ahead of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.4333489733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski030.m4a",
      "text": "でも、皆で頑張れば……\n神頼みが成就する日もきっと来るって信じてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if we all work hard…\nI believe the day will come when our prayers to the gods will be answered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 275.6000136055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_03-ski031.m4a",
      "text": "ですから……神様には、こうお願いしておきます\n月ストの皆と、もっともっと飛躍出来ますようにと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… this is what I’ll ask of the gods.\nThat Moon Tempest‚ all of us‚ can soar even higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.8000176744,
      "sfxList": []
